snippet.title: BBC Radio 1
snippet.description:
The world's best radio station, bringing you the biggest pop acts, the freshest new music and many moments of joy and hilarity.

Listen live online and find out more at www.bbc.co.uk/radio1.

Subscribe to us now to join the Radio 1 YouTube family and never miss out on any of our beautiful videos!
